---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service | PDF Editor">
  <div class="py-24 bg-white flex-1">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl prose prose-slate">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 text-slate-900">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Use of Service</h2>
        <p>You agree to use the service only for lawful purposes. You are strictly prohibited from using our service to process illegal, copyrighted, or malicious documents.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>The service is provided "as is". We make no warranties, expressed or implied, and hereby disclaim and negate all other warranties including, without limitation, implied warranties or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>